              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>often</Gloss>
                <Gloss>many times</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>It is also possible to understand {L:πολυμερῶς&lt;SDBG:πολυμερῶς:000000&gt;}[a] ({D:58.29}). Some scholars, however, understand {L:πολυμερῶς&lt;SDBG:πολυμερῶς:000000&gt;} in the sense of ‘fragmentary’ (see {D:63.19}). For yet another interpretation of {L:πολυμερῶς&lt;SDBG:πολυμερῶς:000000&gt;} in {S:05800100100002}, see {D:89.81}.</Comments>
